sentences: He worked for two months at American Apparel who later fired him for being homeless.
In 2012, "Flunky Flex", the first song Crow ever wrote was released on an OWSLA compilation album.
After seven months of saving up his money he moved back into his van in Los Angeles and started from scratch.
He released his debut studio album on May 4, 2018, titled The Mystifying Oracle.
